WELCOME TO MY BODY MUSIEUM!
THIS MAP IS A CONSTANT WORK IN PROGRESS,
HOWEVER, I AIM TO ADD AT LEAST 2 NEW
BODYS EVERY WEEK SO THERE WILL BE 
PLENTY TO SEE BY THE YEARS END.

ALL BODYS ON DISPLAY ARE CREATED WITH NO MALICE
INTENDED AND REFLECT MY SENSE OF HUMOR RATHER
THAN THE PEOPLE THEY LOOSLY MIMIC.

ALTERNATIVELY, IF A BOOTLEG OF YOUR BODY
IS ON DISPLAY THAT YOU WOULD RATHER NOT
BE THERE, PLEASE LET ME KNOW AND I WILL 
REMOVE IT.

IF YOU WOULD LIKE A BOOTLEG VERSION OF YOUR
BODY MADE, FEEL FREE TO ASK ME ' IN PERSON'.
YOU MAY ALSO DONATE YOUR BODY FOR 'BETTER
RESULTS' ALTHOUGH THIS IS OPTIONAL.
